title: Dawes band logo font
content:
Anyone know what font this is?

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20140929075715im_/http:/typophile.com/files/png-1_4223.png)
author: dontbugme

comments.content: At first glance, looks like [Caslon Graphique](http://web.archive.org/web/20140929075715/http:/www.myfonts.com/search/caslon+graphique) but some details differ. [Cabernet](http://web.archive.org/web/20140929075715/http:/marketplace.veer.com/font/Cabernet-Complete-JBT0001003) is also very close but lack a bit of contrast.
Finally I got it! I was not so far with Caslon Graphique. It is [Caslon](http://web.archive.org/web/20140929075715/http:/www.photolettering.com/a/jie1dba) by PLINC.
